<node id="Source Program">
  <data key="d0">Source Program</data>
  <data key="d1">content</data>
  <data key="d2">Source Program is the original code written in a source language or programming language, which serves as the primary input in various stages of the software development process. This code is constructed by a programmer and is meant to instruct the computer to carry out specific tasks or operations, but in its raw form, it is not directly executed by hardware.

The Source Program functions as the initial input for translator programs such as interpreters and compilers. When provided to an interpreter, the source program is read, interpreted, and executed. Some interpreters carry out interpretation and execution simultaneously, meaning the source code is processed line by line or statement by statement, and the specified actions are performed directly as the program runs. When provided to a compiler, the source program is analyzed and translated into machine code or another intermediate form, which can then be executed at a later time.

In summary, the Source Program refers to the original written instructions, created in a human-readable programming language, which serve as input for processes such as interpretation or compilation, ultimately enabling computer systems to perform the intended operations specified by programmers.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-524488f325e3b749520b26154058ac49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d3f98c0ae34a8f4f3f8c11b867518860&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9868a82502f630570f76085c32ca9c42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-581187ec0bef8a2764aaa3dfc31d025f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6ae570a6024d0437660a6a182fb25b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8333ee0b29cc3d6c26d7600e3bfc8036&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f08353c19b24de85f14c2908e06d8312&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d08d8e4136ef0aa05f56218c9bf547a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9ca390783bdb296cb9297d2e99a9290&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad5db227590bab1f4d1b31b133042a5a</data>
  <data key="d4">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d5">1781618652</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="Target Language">
  <data key="d0">Target Language</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Target language is the language into which a translator or compiler converts the source program.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-524488f325e3b749520b26154058ac49</data>
  <data key="d4">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
