<node id="Chinese University MOOC">
  <data key="d0">Chinese University MOOC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Chinese University MOOC is an online educational platform, prominently branded as "中国大学MOOC." Serving as a massive open online course (MOOC) provider in China, Chinese University MOOC delivers a wide array of educational content and formal lecture materials. The platform is identified by the presence of its logo, often displayed in the upper right corner of instructional slides or images, signaling its official association with the provided lecture content.

As a leading Chinese MOOC platform, Chinese University MOOC plays the role of both an educational organization and course provider, responsible for making high-quality university-level courses accessible online. It connects learners with diverse academic resources, indicated by the distinctive branding or gray logo visible on educational materials. The platform’s consistent visual identity across lecture slides signifies formal academic context and marks Chinese University MOOC as the source of the instructional materials.</data>
