<node id="Result">
  <data key="d0">Result</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">Result is the output or effect produced as the final outcome of processing and executing a computer program. Specifically, in the context of machine language and high-level language programming, Result refers to the output that is yielded after a high-level language program is compiled into machine language and then executed. This process involves compiling the source program into a machine language program, which is subsequently run to produce the Result.

Result can also denote the outcome generated by executing a machine language program that was created through compilation from a high-level source. In diagrammatic or flowchart representations—such as those often found in educational slides or documentation—Result is typically labeled as the output product or final effect within the process, following compilation and execution stages.

Additionally, Result may refer to the output obtained after a source program is interpreted and executed directly by an interpreter, bypassing the separate compilation phase. In such scenarios, Result still encapsulates the final outcome or effect produced by the program’s execution, regardless of whether this involved compilation to machine code or interpretation of the source code.

Thus, Result comprehensively represents the final output or effect generated at the end of executing a program, whether through compilation to machine language or direct interpretation of a source program.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-896812268ddab3f8ba43e409ef31f0f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb64dc11aeecd21521a2af6a8cfa8093&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecf31faebdcc696eee3f0300603ac136&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8151fd6721162afb5261395661b1280c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed7293e9aeec5ea94f7f86f4ae119370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5b7ce5bd1723067a738bbe62a548e6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-769c2785e5eaa135d71c12ae137012bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4e6dd16b5efe88951506ef1089b4714&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-be01738fa65ffd9fde1205d015283524&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a29dd8f170730feb43137deb71f6861&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6737524161da7d35b4f23f14c5047487&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58f59c2e670bb8779699efd00a5d0689&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-006cd400ede79791d562a634055a0181&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ab812108c1d67da8cf205eff9b21211&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-939c20c7d9cbf4dcc11abf5ae47b2975&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b141de5784e7c358ae42229b3b2f7482&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea5501cfc173617b2419abd0158aae03&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad5db227590bab1f4d1b31b133042a5a</data>
