  <data key="d2">中国大学MOOC is a prominent Chinese Massive Open Online Course (MOOC) provider and online educational platform. It is widely recognized for delivering a variety of online courses, typically through video lectures and slide presentations. The platform's branding is consistently present, with its logo frequently appearing in the top right corner of lecture slides and video frames, clearly indicating the source and context of the presentation materials.

As an educational organization, 中国大学MOOC serves as a key provider of online academic content, supporting distance learning for a broad audience. The presence of its logo on course materials signifies authenticity and association with the platform, ensuring that users can easily identify the origin of the online courses and lectures.</data>
