<node id="Machine Code">
  <data key="d0">Machine Code</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Machine Code is a form of low-level programming language into which compilers translate high-level languages, suitable for execution by computers.&lt;SEP&gt;Machine code is a type of low-level programming language referenced as one possible output of a compiler.</data>
