<node id="China University MOOC">
  <data key="d0">China University MOOC</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">China University MOOC is a Chinese online education platform and academic organization that provides massive open online courses (MOOCs) at the university level. It serves as both the provider and host for a wide range of recorded lectures and educational content, including specific subject areas such as compilers. The platform is frequently identified by its distinctive logo, which appears in the upper or top right corner of educational lecture slides, presentation slides, video frames, or related images, signifying its association with and authorship of the educational materials.

As an educational platform, China University MOOC delivers online courses and tutorial videos that are widely used in university-level teaching. The consistent appearance of its logo or watermark on instructional material indicates that the lectures, presentations, and courses are produced, hosted, or presented by the organization. Through its services, China University MOOC plays a significant role in the dissemination of higher education content to learners, supporting academic instruction and online learning across various disciplines.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-ecf31faebdcc696eee3f0300603ac136&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8151fd6721162afb5261395661b1280c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed7293e9aeec5ea94f7f86f4ae119370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4e6dd16b5efe88951506ef1089b4714&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58f59c2e670bb8779699efd00a5d0689&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b141de5784e7c358ae42229b3b2f7482&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9868a82502f630570f76085c32ca9c42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-581187ec0bef8a2764aaa3dfc31d025f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f08353c19b24de85f14c2908e06d8312&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d08d8e4136ef0aa05f56218c9bf547a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ea5501cfc173617b2419abd0158aae03&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-4a520ba50261026796d23e33d0ff1338&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dd1dcbe9ff39952732386923ec86087&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-1bfe52cdac907ea3845166a1ce078018&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-826aa36e7f937baaf856dfeacfad25eb&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-293989abe9dcdef47c800cf7a0bb7139&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d42ba5c90b44608bf31c83a6aaefab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7411d36d649aafe21488e517462ac4f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a37a212e987f64c641f183a6193b17ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10157605ebc9330ac206f46361e0d49</data>
