<node id="Interpretation">
  <data key="d0">Interpretation</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">Interpretation, in the context of computer science and programming language theory, refers to a method of executing and managing source code by translating and running instructions directly, typically line by line, at runtime. Unlike compilation, which involves converting the entire source program into a target language or intermediate form prior to execution, interpretation processes source code incrementally or step by step during program execution. This approach enables immediate output and does not require generating an intermediate file or performing a separate translation phase before execution begins.

In this model, an interpreter reads each instruction in the source code and executes or evaluates it on the fly, without the need for prior conversion into another language or binary form. As a result, interpretation allows for direct interaction with the program, facilitating real-time feedback and dynamic execution. It is frequently discussed as a contrasting approach to compilation, representing an alternative mode of program translation and execution. Educational materials and lecture slides often highlight interpretation as one of the principal models for processing programming languages, commonly presenting it in opposition to compilation to clarify its unique operational characteristics.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-3d950de84d0ab1b843f90c017307ca7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc049639d1e1e566c66a22d0fbe3bc50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dd1dcbe9ff39952732386923ec86087&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e819693926847d8f479788882292021a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9e9a810e3a5028090fbec9f995e208e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-bccc9e3f7bce263dd0635fc2e0341663&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-293989abe9dcdef47c800cf7a0bb7139&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d98cddba973b8d1706698f34f22c1fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-47d42ba5c90b44608bf31c83a6aaefab&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7411d36d649aafe21488e517462ac4f4&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b502762bbfbf1513c1ccaa956b9f21f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a37a212e987f64c641f183a6193b17ce&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c10157605ebc9330ac206f46361e0d49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2dd190a00f87ac9b0e3de713356629d2</data>
  <data key="d4">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d5">1781618667</data>
