<edge source="Interpreter" target="Translator Program">
  <data key="d7">1.0</data>
  <data key="d8">An interpreter is another type of translator program, distinct from a compiler.</data>
  <data key="d9">category,distinction</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-524488f325e3b749520b26154058ac49</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781614991</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Interpreter" target="Source Program">
  <data key="d7">10.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation "(Interpreter, Source Program)" describes the connection in which an interpreter receives the source program as its input. An interpreter operates by taking the source program and directly processing, interpreting, and executing its instructions without generating an intermediate or complete target program. Rather than compiling the entire source code into a separate executable or target language before execution, the interpreter reads the source program, interprets its commands, and executes them sequentially as part of its primary task.

This direct execution process means that the interpreter does not produce a separate output program; instead, it continuously interprets instructions from the source program and carries them out immediately. The interpreter relies fundamentally on the source program as its input and serves as the mechanism responsible for turning the program's written instructions into real-time computational actions. As a result, the relation between interpreter and source program is exemplified by the interpreter's unique capability to process and execute code on-the-fly, without the need for prior compilation or target program generation.</data>
  <data key="d9">execution,input,interpretation,processing,program execution,program operation,programming,programming process,translation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-524488f325e3b749520b26154058ac49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-d3f98c0ae34a8f4f3f8c11b867518860&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9868a82502f630570f76085c32ca9c42&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-581187ec0bef8a2764aaa3dfc31d025f&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e6ae570a6024d0437660a6a182fb25b3&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8333ee0b29cc3d6c26d7600e3bfc8036&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f08353c19b24de85f14c2908e06d8312&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5d08d8e4136ef0aa05f56218c9bf547a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-c9ca390783bdb296cb9297d2e99a9290&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ad5db227590bab1f4d1b31b133042a5a</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781619175</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
