  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Interpreter operates by interpreting and executing the source code simultaneously, processing each line in real time.&lt;SEP&gt;An interpreter uses the method of interpreting and executing source code simultaneously, rather than compiling.&lt;SEP&gt;Interpreter implements the method of interpreting and executing source code simultaneously.&lt;SEP&gt;Interpreter is defined by the method of interpreting and executing program code simultaneously.</data>
  <data key="d9">execution,method,method characteristics,process,program execution</data>
