<edge source="Compiler" target="High-Level Programming Language">
  <data key="d7">3.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A compiler analyzes source programs written in high-level programming languages.&lt;SEP&gt;Compiler takes high-level programming language as input for translation.&lt;SEP&gt;Compiler converts high-level programming language code into low-level programming language code.</data>
  <data key="d9">analysis,code translation,input,program conversion,transformation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-524488f325e3b749520b26154058ac49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8151fd6721162afb5261395661b1280c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ab812108c1d67da8cf205eff9b21211</data>
