  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Compiler" target="Low-Level Programming Language">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A compiler translates high-level language programs into low-level programming languages.&lt;SEP&gt;Compiler translates high-level code into a low-level programming language.&lt;SEP&gt;Compiler produces low-level programming language as output after translation.&lt;SEP&gt;Compiler produces low-level programming language output from high-level language input.</data>
  <data key="d9">code translation,compilation output,output,transformation,translation</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-524488f325e3b749520b26154058ac49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb64dc11aeecd21521a2af6a8cfa8093&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8151fd6721162afb5261395661b1280c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ab812108c1d67da8cf205eff9b21211</data>
