<edge source="Compiler" target="Host Machine">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The host machine runs the compiler during the compilation process.&lt;SEP&gt;The host machine is the computer where the compiler is executed.&lt;SEP&gt;The compiler operates on the host machine when converting code.&lt;SEP&gt;The host machine is the environment on which the compiler operates.</data>
  <data key="d9">compilation location,execution environment,hosting,platform,processing</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-524488f325e3b749520b26154058ac49&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2693f7eed941d7a575fb48103191b9f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-be01738fa65ffd9fde1205d015283524&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a29dd8f170730feb43137deb71f6861</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
