<edge source="Compiler" target="High-Level Language Program">
  <data key="d7">18.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (Compiler, High-Level Language Program) describes the interaction whereby a compiler operates on a high-level language program. Specifically, the compiler takes a high-level language program, often referred to as the source code, as its input during the compilation or translation process. This program is typically written in a human-readable format, making it easier for programmers to develop complex software.

Upon receiving the high-level language program, the compiler processes and translates this input into a low-level language program, which could be a machine language or another form of lower-level code. This translation is essential to enable execution by computer hardware, as machines cannot directly interpret high-level instructions. Throughout the compilation process, the high-level language program consistently serves as the initial source code input for the compiler, initiating and directing the entire sequence of translation.</data>
  <data key="d9">code input,code transformation,code translation,compilation,compilation process,input,input conversion,input-output,program transformation,programming,source,source program,syntax conversion,transformation,translates,translation,translation process</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-aa6a6137fde10652cd93a8bcf9ffebcf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896812268ddab3f8ba43e409ef31f0f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-cb64dc11aeecd21521a2af6a8cfa8093&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecf31faebdcc696eee3f0300603ac136&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8151fd6721162afb5261395661b1280c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed7293e9aeec5ea94f7f86f4ae119370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5b7ce5bd1723067a738bbe62a548e6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-769c2785e5eaa135d71c12ae137012bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4e6dd16b5efe88951506ef1089b4714&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2693f7eed941d7a575fb48103191b9f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-be01738fa65ffd9fde1205d015283524&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a29dd8f170730feb43137deb71f6861&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6737524161da7d35b4f23f14c5047487&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58f59c2e670bb8779699efd00a5d0689&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-006cd400ede79791d562a634055a0181&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-939c20c7d9cbf4dcc11abf5ae47b2975&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b141de5784e7c358ae42229b3b2f7482</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781618711</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
<edge source="Compiler" target="Low-Level Language Program">
  <data key="d7">12.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (Compiler, Low-Level Language Program) describes the process in which a compiler transforms input written in a high-level programming language into an output program written in a low-level language. Specifically, the compiler accepts a high-level language program or source code as input and, through a process known as translation, converts it into an equivalent low-level language program. This resulting low-level program may be in forms such as assembly code or machine code.

The low-level language program produced by the compiler serves as an executable or near-executable version of the original high-level program, retaining equivalence in logic and behavior. The output of the compiler is fundamentally the direct product of processing and translating the high-level source code, ensuring the semantics of the original program are preserved in its low-level representation. This process is essential for enabling code written in human-readable high-level languages to be executed by computer hardware, which operates based on low-level instructions.</data>
  <data key="d9">code output,code translation,conversion,output,output generation,program transformation,target output,translates,translation,translation process</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-aa6a6137fde10652cd93a8bcf9ffebcf&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-896812268ddab3f8ba43e409ef31f0f6&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ecf31faebdcc696eee3f0300603ac136&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed7293e9aeec5ea94f7f86f4ae119370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e5b7ce5bd1723067a738bbe62a548e6b&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-769c2785e5eaa135d71c12ae137012bd&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4e6dd16b5efe88951506ef1089b4714&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2693f7eed941d7a575fb48103191b9f7&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-2a29dd8f170730feb43137deb71f6861&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-58f59c2e670bb8779699efd00a5d0689&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-006cd400ede79791d562a634055a0181&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b141de5784e7c358ae42229b3b2f7482</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781618718</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
