<edge source="Host Machine" target="Cross Compiler">
  <data key="d7">4.0</data>
  <data key="d8">A cross compiler runs on the host machine.&lt;SEP&gt;A cross compiler operates on a host machine to produce code for a different target machine.&lt;SEP&gt;The cross compiler generates machine code for a target machine while running on a host machine.&lt;SEP&gt;Host Machine is where a cross compiler operates to produce machine code for the target machine.</data>
