<edge source="Machine Language Program" target="Result">
  <data key="d7">9.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The relation (Machine Language Program, Result) denotes the process whereby the execution of a machine language program leads to the production of a result. This relationship highlights the procedural flow in which a machine language program, when run or executed, culminates in generating a result or reaching the result stage.

According to various descriptions, multiple diagrams and visualizations such as flow diagrams and slide diagrams illustrate this process, indicating its significance in understanding program execution. The core premise is that the running or execution of a machine language program directly yields a result, marking the transition from program instructions to tangible outcome. This relation succinctly conveys how the computational mechanism unfolds: a machine language program is implemented at the hardware level, and upon its completion, it produces the result as the final output.</data>
  <data key="d9">consequence,execution,outcome,output,process output,program output</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-cb64dc11aeecd21521a2af6a8cfa8093&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-8151fd6721162afb5261395661b1280c&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-ed7293e9aeec5ea94f7f86f4ae119370&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-e4e6dd16b5efe88951506ef1089b4714&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-be01738fa65ffd9fde1205d015283524&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-6737524161da7d35b4f23f14c5047487&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9ab812108c1d67da8cf205eff9b21211&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-939c20c7d9cbf4dcc11abf5ae47b2975&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-b141de5784e7c358ae42229b3b2f7482</data>
  <data key="d11">1.1.1 什么是编译程序.mp4</data>
  <data key="d12">1781618762</data>
  <data key="d13"></data>
</edge>
