<edge source="Test: Compilation Vs. Interpretation" target="Interpretation">
  <data key="d7">5.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Test: Compilation Vs. Interpretation examines and contrasts the method of interpretation.&lt;SEP&gt;Test: Compilation Vs. Interpretation includes and discusses the concept of interpretation in programming.&lt;SEP&gt;Test: Compilation Vs. Interpretation sets up a comparison between the concept of interpretation and other methods in computing.&lt;SEP&gt;Test: Compilation Vs. Interpretation involves explaining and contrasting the concept of interpretation.&lt;SEP&gt;Test: Compilation Vs. Interpretation serves as the title, directing focus to Interpretation as a lesson topic.</data>
  <data key="d9">comparison,computer science,computing,concept comparison,concept contrast,educational focus,lesson topic,programming education</data>
  <data key="d10">chunk-3d950de84d0ab1b843f90c017307ca7e&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-fc049639d1e1e566c66a22d0fbe3bc50&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-5dd1dcbe9ff39952732386923ec86087&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-9d98cddba973b8d1706698f34f22c1fe&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-7411d36d649aafe21488e517462ac4f4</data>
